
The make file is located in the same directory

Before compiling the code, make sure the OpenGL MATH library


Change the directory in line 33 and line 48 in main.cpp to your local directory (hard coded for now.... will change soon)

Following are the procedures to compile, link and run the code.



1. $ make 

2. $ ./rpi-sim    



Features: 

1. No C++ class, only C structures, should be friendly for mapping to GPU
2. Only dependent on GLM library, which also supports cuda


